<para style="q1">

<verse number="25" style="v" />I was young and now am old;</para>

<para style="q1">I have never seen the righteous person abandoned</para>

<para style="q1">or his children begging for bread.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="26" style="v" />All the day long he is gracious and lends,</para>

<para style="q1">and his children become a blessing.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="27" style="v" />Turn away from evil and do what is right;</para>

<para style="q1">then you will be safe forever.</para>
